---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Transforming Community
description: Resources for reflection, engagement, and facilitation in the shared work of forming community
---

<div class="endorsement-page shelf-page">

  <p class="essay-back"><a href="/">← Back to Home</a></p>

  <div class="endorsement-layout shelf-layout">

    <aside class="endorsement-nav shelf-nav">
      <h1>Transforming Community</h1>

      <p class="endorsement-subtitle shelf-subtitle">
        A working space for materials intended not only to be read, but to be used—resources
        shaped by memory, experience, and the rhythms of life together, inviting participation
        in the formation of community over time.
      </p>

      <div class="endorsement-nav-group shelf-nav-group">
        <button class="endorsement-nav-toggle shelf-nav-toggle" type="button" aria-expanded="true">
          Reflection
        </button>
        <div class="endorsement-nav-menu shelf-nav-menu">
          <ul class="link-list">
            <li><span>Additional work forthcoming</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="endorsement-nav-group shelf-nav-group">
        <button class="endorsement-nav-toggle shelf-nav-toggle" type="button" aria-expanded="true">
          Engagement
        </button>
        <div class="endorsement-nav-menu shelf-nav-menu">
          <ul class="link-list">
            <li><span>Additional work forthcoming</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="endorsement-nav-group shelf-nav-group">
        <button class="endorsement-nav-toggle shelf-nav-toggle" type="button" aria-expanded="true">
          Facilitation
        </button>
        <div class="endorsement-nav-menu shelf-nav-menu">
          <ul class="link-list">
            {% for item in collections.transformingCommunity %}
              <li><a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.data.title }}</a></li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <main class="endorsement-main shelf-main">

      <section class="endorsement-feature shelf-feature panel">
        <h2>Featured Works</h2>

        {% for item in collections.transformingCommunity %}
          {% if loop.index0 < 3 %}
            <div class="endorsement-feature-excerpt shelf-feature-excerpt">
              <p>
                <strong><a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.data.title }}</a></strong><br>
                {{ item.data.description or item.data.subtitle or "" }}
              </p>
            </div>
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </section>

      <section class="endorsement-howto shelf-howto panel">
        <h2>About This Section</h2>
        <p>
          This shelf gathers materials intended to support the work of remembering, reconnecting,
          and forming community. Some pieces are reflective in tone; others are designed for shared
          use in study, conversation, worship, or group facilitation.
        </p>
        <p>
          The aim is not merely to collect writings, but to offer resources that can be taken up
          in settings where memory has frayed, connection has weakened, or the work of communal
          life needs renewed attention. In that sense, this shelf is less a reading room than a
          working space for reflection, engagement, and facilitation.
        </p>
      </section>

    </main>

  </div>
</div>

{% include "partials/shelf-script.njk" %}